description: This is a skill I made so I can learn the fundamental's of the Amazon Alexa Skills kit. It's based on SpaceGeek & it tells a person some really interesting facts related to technology. It uses the AlexaSkills.js file and picks a random fact to tell the user. Thank You :)
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask techie facts for a fact
Alexa, ask techie facts for a tech fact
Alexa, ask techie facts give me some tech information
name: TechieFacts
shortDescription: This is an Alexa Skill that gives the user a tech fact.
